p-1030976.aspx |title=Keck's Exclusives: Scoop on Modern Family, Army Wives and More - Today's News: Our Take |publisher=TV Guide |date=2011-03-22 |accessdate=2013-07-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130605153628/http://www.tvguide.com/news/kecks-exclusives-scoop-1030976.aspx |archivedate=2013-06-05 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。据在《摩登家庭》中扮演曼尼的里克·罗德里格兹表示，这条狗可能会出现在本季的最后三集中，而且在下一季中会在多集里出场，这条狗的表现也非常好<ref name="tvguide" />。

==反响==
===收视率===
《好警察坏狗狗》于2011年5月11日通过美国广播公司在美国首播，共有约1011.3万户家庭观看，在18-49岁年龄段中收视率为4.2 / 11%<ref name="tvratings">{{cite web |last=Gorman |first=Bill |url=http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2011/05/12/tv-ratings-wednesday-american-idol-rises-dominates-survivor-cm-suspect-behavior-hit-lows/92296/ |title=TV Ratings Wednesday: ‘American Idol’ Rises, Dominates; ‘Survivor,’ ‘CM: Suspect Behavior’ Hit Lows - Ratings | TVbytheNumbers |publisher=Tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com |date=2011-01-25 |accessdate=2013-07-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121015213527/http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2011/05/12/tv-ratings-wednesday-american-idol-rises-dominates-survivor-cm-suspect-behavior-hit-lows/92296/ |archivedate=2012-10-15 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。这个数据的意思是在全国所有18-49岁人群中有4.2%观看了这集节目，而在所有当时有看电视的18-49岁人群中，则有11%是选择收看《好警察坏狗狗》。与上一集《母亲节》相比，本集的收视成绩有8%的升幅<ref name="tvratings" /><ref name="tvratingsfinal">{{cite web |last=Seidman |first=Robert |url=http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2011/05/05/wednesday-final-ratings-american-idol-survivor-modern-family-law-breaking-in-adjusted-down/91702/ |title=Wednesday Final Ratings: ‘American Idol,’ ‘Survivor,’ ‘Modern Family,’ ‘Law & Order: SVU’ Adjusted Up; ‘Breaking In’ Adjusted Down - Ratings | TVbytheNumbers |publisher=Tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com |date=2011-02-27 |accessdate=2013-07-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120731040010/http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2011/05/05/wednesday-final-ratings-american-idol-survivor-modern-family-law-breaking-in-adjusted-down/91702/ |archivedate=2012-07-31 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。在其播出的时间段里，只有[[福克斯广播公司|福克斯广播公司]]的选季节目《[[美国偶像|美国偶像]]》以18-49年年龄段观众中6.9 / 20%的收视率超过《好警察坏狗狗》<ref name="tvratingsfinal"/>，但本集是其播出的这个星期里18-49岁观众人数最多的剧本节目，如果在所有类型节目中按所有年龄段观众计算则排在第23位<ref>{{cite web |last=Seidman |first=Robert |url=http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2011/05/17/tv-ratings-broadcast-top-25-american-idol-the-voice-modern-family-dancing-with-the-stars-ncis-top-week-34-viewing/92944/ |title=TV Ratings Broadcast Top 25: ‘American Idol,’ ‘The Voice,’ ‘Modern Family,’ ‘Dancing with the Stars,’ ‘NCIS’ Top Week 34 Viewing - Ratings | TVbytheNumbers |publisher=Tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com |date=2007-08-28 |accessdate=2013-07-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121016131930/http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2011/05/17/tv-ratings-broadcast-top-25-american-idol-the-voice-modern-family-dancing-with-the-stars-ncis-top-week-34-viewing/92944/ |archivedate=2012-10-16 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。如果增加通过[[数字视频录像机|数字视频录像机]]观看的观众，那么在18-49岁观众群中的收视人数将增加到6.5%<ref>{{cite web |last=Gorman |first=Bill |url=http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2011/05/31/live7-dvr-ratings-modern-family-tops-absolute-gains-gossip-girl-tops-gains/94243/ |title=Live+7 DVR Ratings: ‘Modern Family’ Tops Absolute Gains, ‘Gossip Girl’ Tops % Gains - Ratings | TVbytheNumbers |publisher=Tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com |date=2011-05-26 |accessdate=2013-07-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121017130910/http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2011/05/31/live7-dvr-ratings-modern-family-tops-absolute-gains-gossip-girl-tops-gains/94243/ |archivedate=2012-10-17 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

===评价===
[[Image:Ty_Burrell_2010.jpg|200px]]
《好警察坏狗狗》获得了较为正面的专业评业，许多人都称赞了泰·布利尔的表演。《[[娱乐周刊|娱乐周刊]]》的莱斯利·萨维奇（{{lang|en|Lesley Savage}}）赞扬了这一集的主题，认为“今晚这个角色互换绝对不是什么含蓄的主题，而仍然是非常巧妙的（主意）”<ref name="ew">{{cite web |last=Semigran |first=Aly |url=http://tvrecaps.ew.com/recap/modern-family-season-2-episode-22/ |title=Modern Family recap: Trading Places | Season 2 Episode 22 | EW.com |publisher=Tvrecaps.ew.com |date= |accessdate=2013-07-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120328015536/http://tvrecaps.ew.com/recap/modern-family-season-2-episode-22/ |archivedate=2012-03-28 |deadurl=no }}</ref>，她称布利尔是“最有价值演员”（{{lang|en|MVP}}），表示“当他从屋顶跳到车上那一刻，我差点（笑）死掉了”<ref name="ew"/>。[[影音俱乐部|影音俱乐部]]的唐娜·褒曼（{{lang|en|Donna Bowman}}）认为这一集在半个小时的时间里平等地展现出了编剧和演员所闪烁的光辉<ref name="avclub">{{cite web |last=Bowman |first=Donna |url=http://www.avclub.com/articles/good-cop-bad-dog,55811/ |title="Good Cop Bad Dog" | Modern Family | TV Club | TV |publisher=The A.V. Club |date= |accessdate=2013-07-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121011152817/http://www.avclub.com/articles/good-cop-bad-dog%2C55811/ |archivedate=2012-10-11 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。不过她也批评米歇尔和卡梅隆的桥段缺乏让人感到温馨的内容<ref name="avclub" />。褒曼最终给这集B+的评分，而她这篇文章的读者给出的评价是B<ref name="avclub"/>。《[[纽约_(杂志)|纽约]]》的雷切尔·马杜克斯（{{lang|en|Rachael Maddux}}）称赞这一集“揭示了多个人物的多个新层面”，表示自己对《摩登家庭》近来最满意的表现都是来源于从这些角色身上发现的新内容<ref>{{cite web |last=Maddux |first=Rachael |url=http://www.vulture.com/2011/05/modern_family_recap_8.html |title=Modern Family Recap: I Drink Your Milkshake - Vulture |publisher=Nymag.com |date= |accessdate=2013-07-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130425193101/http://www.vulture.com/2011/05/modern_family_recap_8.html |archivedate=2013-04-25 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

[[有线新闻网|有线新闻网]]评论员亨利·汉克斯（{{lang|en|Henry Hanks}}）写道，“[[星期三|星期三]]晚上的《摩登家庭》是这个系列剧集处于颠峰状态的一个例证。”<ref name="cnn">{{cite web |url=http://marquee.blogs.cnn.com/2011/05/12/modern-family-good-cops-bad-cops-and-gaga/ |title='Modern Family': Good cops, bad cops and Gaga – The Marquee Blog - CNN.com Blogs |publisher=CNN |date= |accessdate=2011-05-19 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121022075236/http://marquee.blogs.cnn.com/2011/05/12/modern-family-good-cops-bad-cops-and-gaga/ |archivedate=2012-10-22 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。他也称布利尔是“本周最有价值演员”<ref name="cnn" />。电视小队（{{lang|en|TV Squad}}）的乔尔·凯勒（{{lang|en|Joel Keller}}）称赞了菲尔和克莱尔的桥段，其中回收使用了标准的电视比喻手段但仍然是“最为好笑的部分”<ref name="tvsquad">{{cite web |url=http://www.aoltv.com/2011/05/12/modern-family-season-2-episode-22-recap/ |title='Modern Family' Season 2, Episode 22 Recap |publisher=Tvsquad.com |date=2011-05-12 |accessdate=2013-07-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120921063938/http://www.aoltv.com/2011/05/12/modern-family-season-2-episode-22-recap/ |archivedate=2012-09-21 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。凯勒批评了米歇尔和卡梅隆的部分情节，因为一方面卡梅隆的疾病导致人物的性格出现变化，二来他还指出，“我觉得要是你能做得够好，那老调重弹也是可以的，但这一次做得不怎么样。”<ref name="tvsquad" />。不过也并非所有的评价都很正面，克丽斯汀·津姆巴（{{lang|en|Christine Ziemba}}）认为这一集“参差不齐”，但“还是有表现不错的时刻”。她也表扬了泰·布利尔的表演，认为他在这一集中非常抢戏<ref name="paste">{{cite web |url=http://www.pastemagazine.com/articles/2011/05/modern-family-review-good-cop-bad-dog-episode-222.html |title=Modern Family Review: "Good Cop Bad Dog" (Episode 2.22) :: TV :: Reviews :: Paste |publisher=Pastemagazine.com |date=2011-05-12 |accessdate=2013-07-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121020153054/http://www.pastemagazine.com/articles/2011/05/modern-family-review-good-cop-bad-dog-episode-222.html |archivedate=2012-10-20 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。津姆巴最终给《好警察坏狗狗》6.9分的评价（最高10分），觉得还算“有头有脸”<ref name="paste"/>。山姆·摩根（{{lang|en|Sam Morgan}}）称赞了编剧的表现，总结认为这集节目虽然很有笑点，但内容上有些过于夸张<ref name="hollywood">{{cite web |url=http://www.hollywood.com/recaps/7793021/modern-family-recap-good-cop-bad-dog |title=Modern Family Recap: Good Cop Bad Dog |publisher=Hollywood.com |date=2011-05-12 |accessdate=2013-07-23 |archive-date=2013-07-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130723100200/http://www.hollywood.com/recaps/7793021/modern-family-recap-good-cop-bad-dog |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

